data.description: Stunning interior remodel & on the most picturesque lot in Monarch Country Club, this gorgeous extended ''Mayfair'' model features a sparkling heated saltwater oversized pool, (screened) located on the 16th green, overlooking tranquil views of water and golf!  This open plan is light and bright, just perfect for entertaining! You will fall in love w/ the glass enclosed lanai! New porcelain tile throughout (24x48), luxurious primary & guest baths, & a stunning new wet bar is sure to delight! Plantation shutters adorn the new windows and impact sliders! Designer kitchen w/dine in area, granite & whirlpool appliances to include 2023 Refrigerator & 2022 Microwave! Fresh interior Paint! NEW pool screens, pool pump, pavers, & epoxy floors in the garage are just a few of the outstanding upgrades Monarch Country Club Regent Membership is transferable from seller, paid in full until October 2024. Not required. Golf, Social, Tennis memberships available! HOA covers common areas, lawn maintenance, the roof cleaned every 2 years, the driveway pressure washed, exterior painted every 6 years, underground utilities, fiberoptic cable TV/Hi-speed internet, & manned security gate. This golf & tennis community is close to 95 and FL TPKE for commuter's delight! Minutes to downtown, beaches, restaurants & shopping! This home shows like a model! Call for your tour today!
